  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Choose one from force- or tech-casting. You've mastered fighting and interfering with casters of the chosen type, confounding their concentration. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>When a creature within 30 feet of you that you can see casts a power, they provoke an opportunity attack from you.</li>\n<li>You have advantage on saving throws against powers cast by creatures you can see if you've dealt damage to them since the start of your last turn.</li>\n<li>Whenever you force a creature to make a saving throw to maintain concentration, the DC for the saving throw increases by an amount equal to your proficiency bonus.</li></ul>",
